comments: Dunn (UTA) is moving alongside Bridges' (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Markkanen (UTA) brings his right hand toward Dinwiddie's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs with Dinwiddie's front at the end of the drive.
Olynyk (UTA) fully extends his hands into Claxton's (BKN) front and initiates contact that alters Claxton's body trajectory during his layup attempt.
Finney-Smith (BKN) turns slightly with his left arm brought toward Horton-Tucker's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs with Horton-Tucker's front/side as he gathers.
Dunn (UTA) engages and disengages with Bridges' (BKN) side, and marginal contact occurs as Bridges slips out of his screening position.
Toscano-Anderson's (UTA) right arm comes forward slightly when marginal contact occurs with Dinwiddie's (BKN) arm/side at the end of his drive and as he gathers.
Johnson (BKN) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Horton-Tucker's (UTA) front during the drive.

Olynyk (UTA) is retreating alongside Claxton's (BKN) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together in the lane. Olynyk then makes clean forearm contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Claxton prior to incidental contact occurring.
Claxton (BKN) and Olynyk (UTA) make incidental arm contact with one another after the ball becomes dislodged.

Dunn (UTA) raises both arms up as he pursues the loose ball and marginal contact occurs with Finney-Smith's (BKN) forearms, causing Finney-Smith to momentarily lose control of the ball, which he quickly recovers.
Toscano-Anderson (UTA) turns into Finney-Smith (BKN) and initiates body contact during Finney-Smith's upward shooting motion.
Olynyk (UTA) and Dinwiddie (BKN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Markkanen (UTA) and O'Neale (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.

Dinwiddie (BKN) is moving alongside Toscano-Anderson's (UTA) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs. Dinwiddie then turns slightly as Toscano-Anderson simultaneously turns into the lane and further marginal body contact occurs prior to Toscano-Anderson's pass.
Olynyk (UTA) commits a take foul on Johnson (BKN).
Bridges (BKN) engages and disengages with Horton-Tucker (UTA) during the inbound.
Johnson (BKN) legally contests Agbaji's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (BKN).
Olynyk (UTA) releases the inbound within five seconds.
Bridges (BKN) commits a take foul on Horton-Tucker (UTA).

Following the inbound, Olynyk (UTA) pursues Curry (BKN) into the backcourt and in an attempt to stop the game clock with a take foul, he swipes down. Olynyk he avoids making contact with Curry. A foul should not have been called.
Johnson (BKN) releases his hand away from Markkanen's (UTA) side and marginal contact occurs as Markkanen elevates for the rebound.
Johnson (BKN) and Curry (BKN) each bring a hand toward Olynyk's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs with Olynyk's front as he dribbles toward the wing in transition.
Curry (BKN) releases his left hand away from Olynyk's (UTA) front and marginal contact occurs as Olynyk starts his upward shooting motion.
